  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
    class DicePanel_V
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    DicePanel_V Shows the state of the dice graphically. Show the numbered dice
    whether it scores,
    whether it is chosen to score.
    Seperate the reserved ones from those that were just rolled.
    Separater is vertical on the right side or separater is horizontal on the bottom.
